text:
="preserve">Image:North High Street, Holyoke MA.jpg|thumb|The North High Street in Holyoke
Holyoke is a city in southwestern Massachusetts. It is close to Springfield. The city was settled in 1745 and incorporated in 1850. Holyoke had almost 40,000 people at the 2010 census.
